select mutiple images:

A user choose mutiple images one by one. The system checks if their extension names are supported.
All the invalid files will not be selected successfully. The system then shows the thumbnails of correct image files.
If the user removes only one images or resets the selection to remove all the selected images, the system will update the state and be ready for the new selection.

view results:

After a successful processing, the user views results of it. 
The system shows the names and percentages of top 4 object classes.
And the system is ready for the next classification.
